summary: This document is a consent form for a resident agent for service of process for a company named Basics VI, LLC, designated by Southern Final LLC. It includes signatures and acknowledgments related to the legal standing of the agent in the Virgin Islands.

persons.name: Brett A. Geary
persons.context: Brett A. Geary is identified as the Notary Public who subscribed and sworn the document.

keyFacts: The document is a consent form for a resident agent for service of process.
Basics VI, LLC is designated by Southern Final LLC as the company for which the agent is acting.
The document was signed on May 25, 2013.
Brett A. Geary is the Notary Public who witnessed the signing.
The document is marked as confidential pursuant to federal criminal procedure.
